1
00:00:39,960 --> 00:00:41,119
The severance pay,

2
00:00:41,560 --> 00:00:42,560
give it to them.

3
00:00:42,560 --> 00:00:43,439
Settle it up.

4
00:00:43,439 --> 00:00:44,039
Sure.

5
00:00:44,479 --> 00:00:45,079
No problem.

6
00:00:45,679 --> 00:00:47,119
I've got more good news.

7
00:00:47,600 --> 00:00:50,960
Once word got out about the free comics,

8
00:00:51,240 --> 00:00:53,560
our pool hall got absolutely swamped.

9
00:00:53,560 --> 00:00:55,799
We're all rolling in cash now.

10
00:00:56,640 --> 00:00:57,320
Hell yeah.

11
00:00:57,679 --> 00:00:58,079
Cheers.

12
00:00:58,439 --> 00:00:59,880
My day has finally come!

13
00:01:08,599 --> 00:01:09,120
Get up.

14
00:01:09,120 --> 00:01:10,640
You're drooling all over.

15
00:01:10,640 --> 00:01:12,599
What? Never seen this before?

16
00:01:13,519 --> 00:01:14,439
Where's the manager?

17
00:01:14,840 --> 00:01:15,599
Manager.

18
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:16,840
Manager.

19
00:01:20,120 --> 00:01:20,879
What's up?

20
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:22,480
How much to dance here all night?

21
00:01:22,959 --> 00:01:23,840
What about her?

22
00:01:24,359 --> 00:01:25,400
Over 300 a night.

23
00:01:25,680 --> 00:01:27,040
I pay the most in the whole city.

24
00:01:31,319 --> 00:01:32,840
Think I could dance here too?

25
00:01:33,640 --> 00:01:34,159
Here.

26
00:01:34,359 --> 00:01:35,239
Not enough?

27
00:01:36,280 --> 00:01:37,079
Take it all then.

28
00:01:39,120 --> 00:01:39,599
That's enough.

29
00:01:40,319 --> 00:01:41,000
Enough already.

30
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:42,840
Bro, you wanna dance?

31
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:43,439
Then dance.

32
00:01:43,840 --> 00:01:44,439
Go ahead and dance.

33
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:49,159
Dali, Dali, give us a dance, Dali!

34
00:01:49,159 --> 00:01:50,359
Come on, join in.

35
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:53,040
Join us!

36
00:02:00,599 --> 00:02:01,280
Come on!

37
00:02:02,519 --> 00:02:04,200
I don't know how to dance.

38
00:02:21,879 --> 00:02:22,439
Hungry?

39
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:25,599
Thanks.

40
00:02:25,599 --> 00:02:26,240
Go on inside and eat.

41
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:37,000
All right then.

42
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:40,479
This place is way too filthy.

43
00:02:40,479 --> 00:02:41,800
There's even a bug in the food!

44
00:02:42,319 --> 00:02:43,159
Let's get out of here.

45
00:02:43,159 --> 00:02:44,400
Never eat at her place again.

46
00:02:44,400 --> 00:02:45,439
I saw it.

47
00:02:45,439 --> 00:02:47,159
He planted that bug himself.

48
00:02:50,759 --> 00:02:52,879
Your man Zhu Yihai is a real menace.

49
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:53,719
This isn't...

50
00:02:53,719 --> 00:02:54,280
...over yet.

51
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:56,639
Put the money down.

52
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:00,639
Let's go.

53
00:03:05,759 --> 00:03:07,280
Auntie, were you just talking about...

54
00:03:07,280 --> 00:03:08,240
Zhu Yihai?

55
00:03:09,199 --> 00:03:10,080
I need to see him.

56
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:11,680
Can you tell me where he is?

57
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:13,360
Why are you looking for him too?

58
00:03:15,639 --> 00:03:16,360
Zhu Yihai!

59
00:03:17,199 --> 00:03:18,439
Keep it down.

60
00:03:18,639 --> 00:03:19,960
Stop making such a racket.

61
00:03:23,280 --> 00:03:23,960
Get up.

62
00:03:25,039 --> 00:03:25,879
Get up!

63
00:03:26,639 --> 00:03:27,400
What are you doing?

64
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:28,800
Who's this?

65
00:03:30,919 --> 00:03:31,599
You're here.

66
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:32,919
What did you come for?

67
00:03:33,199 --> 00:03:34,120
Need something?

68
00:03:35,879 --> 00:03:37,120
Right, right, right.

69
00:03:39,120 --> 00:03:40,360
I'll go get you the money.

70
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:41,919
I don't want your money.

71
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:44,639
You just got the money and now you're returning it?

72
00:03:44,639 --> 00:03:45,520
How are you going to survive?

73
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:46,560
Come on, Qian Huilian.

74
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:47,919
You don't even work here.

75
00:03:47,919 --> 00:03:49,159
Why do you keep coming around?

76
00:03:49,599 --> 00:03:51,000
You think I want to be here?

77
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,240
It's all because of her!

78
00:03:55,879 --> 00:03:57,240
What's the deal with you guys?

79
00:03:57,719 --> 00:03:58,719
A family of three?

80
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:01,400
What's wrong with your head?

81
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:02,360
Zhu Yihai!

82
00:04:02,719 --> 00:04:04,000
Whose kid is this anyway?

83
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:04,439
Well...

84
00:04:04,439 --> 00:04:04,919
I mean...

85
00:04:04,919 --> 00:04:07,319
How am I supposed to know whose kid it is?

86
00:04:08,599 --> 00:04:09,719
What's this button for?

87
00:04:09,719 --> 00:04:10,800
I just let you hold it.

88
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:11,919
Don't press random buttons!

89
00:04:11,919 --> 00:04:13,280
You erased my tape!

90
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:18,480
You're my sister, right?

91
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:20,839
The kid's here looking for her family.

92
00:04:21,759 --> 00:04:22,839
Let me see who her mom is.

93
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:25,240
Hey kid.

94
00:04:25,399 --> 00:04:28,879
Bro, my mom said I can't go to school anymore.

95
00:04:29,399 --> 00:04:30,319
Wait, what happened?

96
00:04:30,319 --> 00:04:32,000
Last night Mom said

97
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:34,600
Dad's truck got seized by the factory.

98
00:04:34,879 --> 00:04:37,600
I have to go work in the city with them.

99
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:39,439
So I can't go to school.

100
00:04:39,439 --> 00:04:40,680
But I don't want to go.

101
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:42,120
I wanted to tell you.

102
00:04:43,839 --> 00:04:45,319
The truck got confiscated?

103
00:04:45,759 --> 00:04:47,160
That damn Ge Zhendong!

104
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:49,079
He's taking his revenge out on us.

105
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:51,920
Brother Hai.

106
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:52,480
Let's round up the guys.

107
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:53,680
What are you doing?

108
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:54,439
Put that down right now!

109
00:04:59,879 --> 00:05:00,399
Kid.

110
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:02,600
Do you want to go to school?

111
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:03,319
Yes.

112
00:05:03,319 --> 00:05:04,199
Why are you asking her that?

113
00:05:04,199 --> 00:05:05,920
She's so young, of course she should be in school.

114
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:09,199
Alright, Ge Zhendong.

115
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:10,759
You've got no shame at all.

116
00:05:11,639 --> 00:05:12,040
Let's go.

117
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,480
Let's go have a chat with him. Move!

118
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:16,360
What about me?

119
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:18,040
You're not running the pool hall anymore?

120
00:05:18,279 --> 00:05:19,079
You stay with his sister.

121
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:20,879
What about her?

122
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:22,480
None of your damn business!

123
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:44,720
What's going on?

124
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:46,160
Ge Zhendong.

125
00:05:46,160 --> 00:05:47,360
Laying off so many people?

126
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:48,920
You're pretty ruthless.

127
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:50,879
No, I'm not.

128
00:05:50,879 --> 00:05:51,639
Beat him up!

129
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:02,399
Those punks really did a number on me.

130
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:08,160
Busy, huh, Director Ge?

131
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:10,720
Bo... Boss Long.

132
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:11,680
What happened to you?

133
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:12,759
Your head's covered in bumps.

134
00:06:12,759 --> 00:06:13,360
Don't even ask.

135
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:13,920
Come on, come on.

136
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:15,319
Please, come inside.

137
00:06:19,639 --> 00:06:21,199
Boss Long, what brings you here?

138
00:06:21,199 --> 00:06:22,040
What's all this about?

139
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:23,120
Where the hell have you been messing around?

140
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:23,600
No, no, no.

141
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,120
I'm too filthy.

142
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:24,839
Have a seat, have a seat.

143
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:30,319
Nice walnuts you've got here, Director Ge.

144
00:06:30,319 --> 00:06:30,759
Right?

145
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:32,439
Here, Boss Long.

146
00:06:33,319 --> 00:06:34,480
Make yourself at home.

147
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:36,879
Boss Long.

148
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:38,480
What brings you here this time?

149
00:06:42,199 --> 00:06:43,399
Here's the thing, Director Ge.

150
00:06:43,879 --> 00:06:45,519
I heard our factory

151
00:06:45,519 --> 00:06:47,120
is running into some financial trouble.

152
00:06:47,639 --> 00:06:49,120
I came to see if I could help.

153
00:06:52,759 --> 00:06:53,839
Boss Long.

154
00:06:53,839 --> 00:06:55,319
Word travels fast with you.

155
00:06:57,680 --> 00:06:58,680
I, Long Xiao,

156
00:06:58,680 --> 00:06:59,959
don't have any special talents.

157
00:07:00,079 --> 00:07:00,959
Just a lot of friends.

158
00:07:01,319 --> 00:07:02,439
But I can't compare to you,

159
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:03,959
Director Ge, with your massive enterprise.

160
00:07:03,959 --> 00:07:04,600
Am I right?

161
00:07:05,040 --> 00:07:05,839
At the factory, I mean,

162
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:07,000
over two thousand workers.

163
00:07:07,399 --> 00:07:08,480
Just the monthly payroll alone,

164
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:10,480
is something I couldn't even fathom.

165
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:11,879
No, no, no.

166
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:17,879
Boss Long.

167
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:19,959
Name your price.

168
00:07:27,079 --> 00:07:27,720
Traitor!

169
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:28,920
Scumbag!

170
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:29,560
Traitor!

171
00:07:30,759 --> 00:07:32,000
Bro, why do I feel like they mean you?

172
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:32,680
No way.

173
00:07:32,959 --> 00:07:34,680
We just sorted out their severance pay.

174
00:07:34,680 --> 00:07:35,319
Who are you talking about?

175
00:07:35,439 --> 00:07:36,800
We mean you two!

176
00:07:37,639 --> 00:07:38,879
Scumbags! Traitors!

177
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:41,279
What's going on, bro?

178
00:07:41,279 --> 00:07:42,319
Run! I'll wait inside!

179
00:07:42,839 --> 00:07:43,480
Don't run!

180
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:44,480
How many workers did you fire?

181
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:45,879
It's all because of you!

182
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:46,519
Run!

183
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:48,680
Stop smashing! Stop!

184
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:49,240
Still smashing?

185
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:54,279
You're a straight shooter, Director Ge.

186
00:07:55,800 --> 00:07:56,519
Here's the thing.

187
00:07:56,720 --> 00:07:57,560
After I went back,

188
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:58,480
I thought it over carefully.

189
00:07:58,920 --> 00:08:00,639
That last price was indeed a bit low.

190
00:08:00,959 --> 00:08:01,439
How about this:

191
00:08:02,439 --> 00:08:03,639
I'll add another million.

192
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:04,759
Six million.

193
00:08:05,399 --> 00:08:06,959
That's my bottom line.

194
00:08:13,120 --> 00:08:14,160
Boss Long.

195
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:15,879
A young man with promise

196
00:08:17,199 --> 00:08:18,639
shouldn't have a bottom line.

197
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:32,279
Director Ge, what are you saying?

198
00:08:32,759 --> 00:08:33,519
Your factory

199
00:08:33,519 --> 00:08:35,679
can't even afford coal for next quarter.

200
00:08:35,679 --> 00:08:36,720
What gives you the right

201
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:38,159
to haggle with me?

202
00:08:38,559 --> 00:08:39,759
Honestly...

203
00:08:42,480 --> 00:08:44,279
"Though humble in rank,

204
00:08:45,039 --> 00:08:46,440
I never forget my country."

205
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:52,360
Ge Zhendong, you're going too far.

206
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:54,639
Showing off those panda eyes?

207
00:08:56,399 --> 00:08:57,600
You're no better yourself.

208
00:08:59,799 --> 00:09:00,840
Brother Yihai.

209
00:09:01,799 --> 00:09:02,960
Boss Long.

210
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:03,799
Why are you here too?

211
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:04,679
Boss Long.

212
00:09:06,159 --> 00:09:06,480
Oh, right.

213
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:07,240
Director Ge,

214
00:09:07,679 --> 00:09:09,159
let me formally introduce you.

215
00:09:09,679 --> 00:09:11,960
This is my good brother, Zhu Yihai.

216
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:12,759
I heard

217
00:09:12,759 --> 00:09:14,480
Director Ge has been taking quite good care of you lately.

218
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:15,639
Yeah.

219
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:16,840
Director Ge.

220
00:09:18,639 --> 00:09:19,159
Right.

221
00:09:19,159 --> 00:09:19,639
Yes.

222
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:22,480
No wonder at this critical juncture,

223
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:23,679
you started demanding severance pay.

224
00:09:24,519 --> 00:09:26,240
Turns out you have a mastermind backing you.

225
00:09:27,279 --> 00:09:27,679
Alright.

226
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:29,120
You two talk.

227
00:09:29,120 --> 00:09:30,080
I won't get in your way.

228
00:09:30,519 --> 00:09:31,080
I'll head out first.

229
00:09:31,240 --> 00:09:31,799
Take care now.

230
00:09:32,639 --> 00:09:33,279
Director Ge,

231
00:09:34,159 --> 00:09:35,120
that contract,

232
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:36,519
think it over quickly.

233
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:39,440
I'm off.

234
00:09:43,559 --> 00:09:44,759
Ge Zhendong, what's your deal?

235
00:09:45,039 --> 00:09:46,320
Confiscating Uncle Wei's truck,

236
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:47,480
That's deliberate payback, huh?

237
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:48,519
Payback?

238
00:09:48,799 --> 00:09:49,960
I wouldn't dare.

239
00:09:50,519 --> 00:09:51,279
Heroes, all of you.

240
00:09:51,519 --> 00:09:52,879
Don't give me that useless crap.

241
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:53,559
Do you know that

242
00:09:53,559 --> 00:09:54,600
you impounded his dad's truck,

243
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:55,960
and now his sister can't even go to school?

244
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:57,320
How could I not know?

245
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:01,000
But if I didn't do that,

246
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:02,639
what was I supposed to do?

247
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:09,080
Yours.

248
00:10:11,480 --> 00:10:12,000
Yours.

249
00:10:15,799 --> 00:10:16,840
I've been craving this for ages.

250
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:19,279
Cheers.

251
00:10:19,679 --> 00:10:20,240
What are you doing?

252
00:10:20,879 --> 00:10:21,679
Spit it out.

253
00:10:21,879 --> 00:10:23,120
What's going on with Zhu Yihai?

254
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:25,679
When we're together,

255
00:10:25,679 --> 00:10:26,879
can we not talk about other people?

256
00:10:29,240 --> 00:10:29,720
Get back here.

257
00:10:30,360 --> 00:10:31,200
Let me tell you,

258
00:10:33,679 --> 00:10:34,840
this time, Zhu Yihai

259
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:35,720
caused a massive mess.

260
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:37,799
What happened?

261
00:10:40,559 --> 00:10:41,840
Does my hair look good?

262
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:43,200
Stop eating.

263
00:10:44,279 --> 00:10:45,399
Last night,

264
00:10:45,399 --> 00:10:46,759
Director Ge told me

265
00:10:46,759 --> 00:10:48,080
he's going to lay off another batch of workers.

266
00:10:48,399 --> 00:10:49,879
Why is he firing people again?

267
00:10:50,159 --> 00:10:51,159
The factory's out of money.

268
00:10:51,159 --> 00:10:52,200
What else can he do but cut them?

269
00:10:56,919 --> 00:10:57,799
Dao Balian.

270
00:10:58,320 --> 00:10:59,720
Nice work.

271
00:10:59,919 --> 00:11:01,559
I don't have a choice either.

272
00:11:02,240 --> 00:11:02,840
Forget it.

273
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:04,720
Starting tomorrow,

274
00:11:04,720 --> 00:11:06,759
you security guys need to step it up.

275
00:11:07,159 --> 00:11:07,919
Don't worry.

276
00:11:08,279 --> 00:11:09,960
I'll make sure to keep Zhu Yihai out.

277
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:11,200
It's not Zhu Yihai.

278
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:12,000
It's someone else.

279
00:11:12,440 --> 00:11:13,039
Someone else?

280
00:11:13,320 --> 00:11:14,039
Who?

281
00:11:15,919 --> 00:11:17,879
I just notified the workers in each workshop.

282
00:11:18,120 --> 00:11:19,039
Cut another ten percent.

283
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:20,279
What?

284
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:22,360
Lay off another ten percent?

285
00:11:22,759 --> 00:11:23,679
Why?

286
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:24,840
Why?

287
00:11:25,919 --> 00:11:27,200
It's all because of you!

288
00:11:27,200 --> 00:11:28,639
How is it because of me?

289
00:11:28,759 --> 00:11:29,759
Listen, Zhu Yihai,

290
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:32,039
quit playing dumb with me, alright?

291
00:11:32,639 --> 00:11:34,399
What are you and Long Xiao scheming?

292
